Add python_requires and Trove classifiers

`python_requires` helps pip ensure the correct version of this package is installed for the user's running Python version.

`classifiers` help make it clear on https://pypi.org which versions are supported.

Assuming the currently-supported Python versions are supported by this project: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/CPython#Version_history
